data.description: Affordable 2 bed 2 bath Village of Howard home in convenient location with easy highway access. Large master suite in upper level with spacious walk-in closet and private full bath. Main floor bedroom and full bath. Oak cabinetry in spacious kitchen. Living room with wood-burning fireplace. 3 seasons room off back of garage that is wired for a hot tub. Finished lower level family room. 2.5 stall detached garage.  Central air and Mitsubishi split(air and heat) also in upper master suite.
